(2396, 517, 1408, 'How are you Henry? Wanted to ask you why did you do a compilation of Igbo proverbs? I\'ve been interested in this part of African culture and I\'m looking to find what makes those who know such things reveal it.', NULL, 0, NULL, 1, '2018-03-18 19:50:18'),
(2397, 542, 1408, 'Etes-vous déjà allé au Congo?', NULL, 0, '', 1, '2018-03-18 20:04:32'),
(2398, 517, 1473, 'Hello Mark. Thanks for your interest.<br />\nFirst of all, I grew up in the village and I was always close to people who grew up in the village. Therefore I am used to  hearing people communicate using Igbo proverbs. I know some of the proverbs by heart, the rest of the proverbs I got from watching movies, reading books and attending cultural festivals.<br />\n<br />\nSecondly, my MA thesis focused upon aspects of the Philosophy of Language. I got to appreciate the complexity of apparently simple linguistic expressions. Each proverb appears to be a well summarized lesson learned from many years of life experience.<br />\n<br />\nI decided to compile 1,000 Igbo proverbs as my contribution to preserving the proverb tradition for the younger generation. <br />\n<br />\n', NULL, 0, '', 1, '2018-03-18 20:08:19'),
