(2401, 517, 1408, 'Ah ok, that\'s very interesting because when I learn about Africa it is the language system which is always impressed upon me. What seems to be very simple phrases or stories tell a deeper story. Now proverbs, from what I know, are the unwritten laws which govern the people of interest. Did you ever experience this yourself?', NULL, 0, '', 1, '2018-03-19 04:05:22'),
