(405, 1668, 'Hello everyone! my Name ist Parfait Ripert Cameroonian living in Germany. <br />\nI m calling on everyone ( diaspora as well as locals) interested in working for Africa to work out with me this big Project.<br />\n my dream is to see a better Africa, the opposite of the continent we see now, a place where everybody will want to leave in. <br />\nI know it sounds crazy and impossible but before I explain how my ideas let me just mention that we have already the knowledge, the capacity, the resource and the will to achieve that. But what we don´t have I guess is the courage to do it. Most of the time we think we don´t have enough power and that most of our governments (corrupted) won´t allow changes to happen. But I guarantee that if the Project is solid and we ( diaspora+ locals) all work together we will be able to build a very sustainable Continent.<br />\n<br />\nSo now to the plan.<br />\nAs we all know, African is the richest continent in terms of Resources but the poorest in terms of economy. so the first thing is to create Jobs, but how can we create Jobs? well, Partnerships create Jobs. Partnerships in/outside Africa. so the organization we will found will look for ways to facilitate partnerships between African companies and governments as well as European companies and Africans governments. No political orientations, only economics relations. so we need  experts from every field (health, education, engineering, business, economy, marketing, etc) <br />\nThe most important purposes  of these partnerships will be: Decrease of immigration to Europe from poor countries (SDG)<br />\n- Decrease of poverty(SDG)<br />\n- Decrease of Hunger<br />\n- Decrease of unemployment<br />\n- Increase affordable clean water<br />\n- Reduction of ground and surface water pollution<br />\n- Increase of good quality farming and agriculture<br />\n- Employment<br />\n- Electricity everywhere<br />\n- Good education(schools)<br />\n<br />\nNow i will just stop here, this is just an overview , there are some other details that can´t be explain here,like how to get the finance or the details of contracts of partenerships etc.. <br />\nI just one everyone interested in that Projet to let me know in comments. Of course it s not yet perfect , it still has some lacks some details i maybe did not take into considerations. so why don´t you come with your knowledge  and your ideas and be part of it.  Be part of the change!<br />\n', NULL, 0, '', 0, '2018-03-11 15:52:05', 0),
(406, 1408, 'Title: Mother, my sweet Mother<br />\n<br />\nAt times the light in her eyes wane,<br />\nFrom a distance it is unclear what is happening,<br />\nIt becomes foggy,<br />\nFrom the boat out at sea where we reside,<br />\nUnfortunate we with a soft cloth dampened by the water of salt,<br />\nThat we should not reach her in her woes,<br />\nTend to her pain on the shores of white sand and trees of palm,<br />\nUnfortunate isn\'t it,<br />\nIn the day she sleeps as do we,<br />\nAt night it is the emanation of water droplets tapping quietly the face of the lake,<br />\nThe rhyming,<br />\nMarimba is telling her story,<br />\nWe are kept awake by her,<br />\nOn this boat sailing nearer and nearer towards her,<br />\nAnd every moment closer I wonder,<br />\nWill she recognize we,<br />\nThe planter of the grains that fed we,<br />\nThe weaver of the satchel that carried us gently,<br />\nThe voice which spoke of the great rift in the stars,<br />\nOf the Sun and Moon,<br />\nAnd of us in it,<br />\nThere is a breeze blowing beneath the arch of the sky,<br />\nA good breeze,<br />\nCarrying my wonders and we towards home,<br />\nWith medicine and a soft cloth,<br />\nTo be the caregivers we were always meant to be,<br />\nHow else would she know our love,<br />\nHow else would she feel our purpose,<br />\nIn this mysterious place underneath the stars.<br />\n<br />\nTitre: Mère, ma douce mère<br />\n<br />\nParfois la lumière dans ses yeux diminue,<br />\nDe loin, on ne sait pas ce qui se passe,<br />\nIl devient brumeux,<br />\nDu bateau sur la mer où nous résidons,<br />\nMalheureux nous avec un chiffon doux humecté par l\'eau de sel,<br />\nQue nous ne devrions pas l\'atteindre dans ses malheurs,<br />\nTend à sa douleur sur les rives du sable blanc et des arbres de palme,<br />\nMalheureux n\'est-ce pas,<br />\nDans la journée, elle dort comme nous,<br />\nLa nuit, c\'est l\'émanation des gouttelettes d\'eau tapant tranquillement la face du lac,<br />\nLes rimes,<br />\nMarimba raconte son histoire,<br />\nNous sommes gardés éveillés par elle,<br />\nSur ce bateau qui navigue de plus en plus près d\'elle,<br />\nEt chaque instant plus proche je me demande,<br />\nVa-t-elle nous reconnaître,<br />\nLe planteur des grains qui nous nourris,<br />\nLe tisserand de la sacoche qui nous portait doucement,<br />\nLa voix qui parlait de la grande faille dans les étoiles,<br />\nDu Soleil et de la Lune,<br />\nEt de nous dedans,<br />\nIl y a une brise qui souffle sous la voûte du ciel,<br />\nUne bonne brise,<br />\nPortant mes merveilles et nous vers la maison,<br />\nAvec des médicaments et un chiffon doux,<br />\nPour être les soignants, nous étions toujours destinés à être,<br />\nComment pourrait-elle connaître notre amour,<br />\nComment autrement sentirait-elle notre but,<br />\nDans cet endroit mystérieux sous les étoiles.', NULL, 0, '', 0, '2018-03-11 16:39:20', 0),
(407, 1, 'PRIVATE INBOX MESSAGING ON HOTSHI/ MESSAGERIE PRIVEE INBOX SUR HOTSHI<br />\n<br />\nOn Hotshi, to start discussing inbox with a user for the first time, one must first add the person to his contacts. So Hotshi has programmed a default message in English that says \"I\'d like to add you to a contact\". This does not mean that the person is asking for your contact information, it simply means that the person wants to add you as a friend so that he/she can chat privately with you.<br />\nSo when you like a user\'s project, you can easily communicate privately inbox with each other.<br />\n*************************************<br />\nSur Hotshi, pour commencer à discuter inbox avec un utilisateur pour la première fois, il faut d\'abord ajouter la personne à ses contacts. Donc Hotshi a programmé un message par défaut en anglais qui dit \"I\'d like to add you as a contact\". Cela ne veut pas dire que la personne demande vos cordonnées de contact, cela veut simplement dire que la personne veut vous ajouter en tant qu\'ami(e) pour pouvoir discuter en privée inbox avec vous.<br />\nDonc si vous aimez le projet d\'un utilisateur, vous pouvez communiquer facilement en privée inbox.<br />\n', 'https://res.cloudinary.com/hotshi/image/upload/v1520804290/posts/crkke29ztsdhrf0o7cxr.jpg', 52886, 'posts/crkke29ztsdhrf0o7cxr', 0, '2018-03-11 21:38:59', 0),
