oad the application, click on the link below<br />\n<br />\nhttps://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=mgks.infeeds.hotshi<br />\n<br />\nKind Regards,<br />\nHotshi Team ', 'https://res.cloudinary.com/hotshi/image/upload/v1522921988/posts/vpwknz70pujdh2mry5xe.jpg', 11781, 'posts/vpwknz70pujdh2mry5xe', 0, '2018-04-05 09:54:24', 0),
